subtitle: Did you know that the Greys, who are the popularly known avatars for aliens or extraterrestrials,
are a group of cloned slaves created by the Ciakhrr Empire in their genetic breeding
programs? Commonly referred to as "Greys" due to their grey and sometimes brown skin
color and slender elongated head features, they typically belong to the reptoid category. However,
there are also smaller populations with insectoid DNA, saurian-amphibian,
or vegetal varieties. They can be categorized by small or tall heights. These beings exhibit
reptilian vertically slit eyes, often concealed behind biometrical dark lenses.
A significant portion of Greys are products of genetic engineering, bio-synthetic entities,
clones, cybernetically enhanced, or integrated into human environments on
conquered planets. Many of the Grey clones are usually emotionless. Their motives vary widely,
with not all being involved in abductions or experimentation, and not all displaying
malevolent tendencies like those from the Orion alliance. For example, the Solipsi Rai, a peaceful
and benevolent species, were coerced and enslaved by the Orion and Ciakhrr empires. Unfortunately,
the Greys as a whole have garnered a negative reputation, primarily due to their association
with reptoids and their penchant for conquest, terrorizing, and enslaving various Grey factions.
Their technology varies from system to system,
but they are interdimensional travelers at the level of Tier
4. Called Zeta Reticulans, Roswell Greys, or simply Grays, these extraterrestrials are defined
by their humanoid forms, exaggerated long limbs, large black eyes, small noses, thin mouths, and,
of course, grey skin or grey clothing. There are mostly two types of Grays: the smaller drone or
lackey type and the more powerful and intelligent Tall Grays. Grays are some of pop culture's most
recognizable representations of extraterrestrial life. But where did this depiction of
extraterrestrials come from, and why are Grays the ones mostly responsible for all the abductions?
Among the myriad races classified as greys, only 27 are known to visit Earth, with 22 actively
engaged for diverse reasons. The story of the greys goes back to the ancient Orion-Lyran wars
spanning multiple galaxies millions of years ago, draconian reptilians engineered various
non-plasmic lifeforms, including grey clones were they were initially enslaved by them.
Eventually, these clones rebelled against the draconian reptilians their creators,
sparking conflicts across Orion and Pleiades, leading to significant losses and dispersal
among the grey clone army. Seeking to preserve their genetic lineage, greys journeyed to Earth,
abducting humans to create hybrids, as seen in the Essasani group, youthful greys with human-like
hair living on a nearby peaceful island planet in the 5th dimension. On their planet, their
frequency vibrates at the 5th level. They have a society that has no war, nor death nor crime,
or poverty. They have one group of appointed councils who represent the people. They're
planet has a nice temperate changes similar to earth however, the oxygen levels are much higher.
They believe in growing higher into dimensions and evolving to heal mother consciousness. There are a
few who monitor and watch earth even communicating to spiritual mediums through frequency vibrations.
These beings have human mothers or fathers on earth and grey DNA of the grey clone species.
Further distinctions among greys include The Ainanna species who are known for collaborating
with the US Government..... next the peaceful and smiling Airk, and the enslaved Do-hu genetically
altered by Orion and Ciakhrr agendas. The Emerther arrived in 1954 on behalf of the Council of the
Five for peaceful purposes, cautioning against the greys and ciakharr. The shambtnhali from
Zeti Reticuli maintain secret underground bases on Earth in cooperation with the US military.
Various factions, such as the Solipsi Rai, have made alliances with empires for technology
exchange, often involving humans. They are cloned slave workers, heavily involved in abductions,
and synthetic lifeforms. The Eban race from Orion collaborates with the cabal
and human military. Essasani hybrids live peacefully on a nearby island planet,
while Elmanuk from Alnair await Earthlings' awakening, these beings are known to visit
earth interdimensionally and plant high vibrational coding into individuals,
once this coding is implanted inside the skull of the individual, it rearranges the cells and
brain for expansion of data and information. This information and data are the keys to
unlocking from the matrix and the individual will be able to articulate the coding of the
galactic federation's information to the masses essentially raising vibrations and channeling
chakras. Indugutk from Orion have treaties with Earth governments, and the Kiily Tokurt engage
in abductions for food and sexual slave trade. Due to the annunaki of nibiru, many greys share
alien DNA with modern humans and if you look closely at a person's skull you can usually see
if that share similar features to greys with large frame of skull or receding forehead.
Hybrids possess alien genetic coding and alien soul matrix, while rebirds another form of hybrid
lack a soul matrix and can have human or reptoid genetic coding. Genetic engineering, particularly
by the ciakharr, results in varying degrees of divergence from human traits, with distinctions
evident in the eyesâ€”a hallmark of their races. The ciakharr employ grey clones for experiments,
including extreme human pain thresholds and soul extraction, often facilitated in North America.
The other classified experiments in area 51 include testing on humans to help the
greys with procreation for hybrid species to live on the planet Essasani. In exchange,
the nations get advanced technology. They have bases in Antarctica alongside many
other Extraterrestrial races. They are everywhere in society
either by using a cloaking technology, or living underground in hollow earth.
Notable encounters, like the Roswell incident of 1947 and the Betty and Barney
Hill abduction in 1961, offer insights into their telepathic and telekinetic
abilities and their affiliation with the Zeta Reticuli star system. Since this date,
their have been countless UFO encounters that have been recorded and hidden from
the public's knowledge and thankfully due to the fair information act records have now been
declassified but not publicized or promoted to media. Either for the public's own good
or more malicious reasons, it is certain that the greys presence are here to stay.
Here is a true story and encounter with the greys from Elena Daanan, an egyptologist,
author and extraterrestrial channeler, where she recounts the most detailed
extraterrestrial abduction by the Ciakhrr Grays, the saving of her life and the hidden
secrets of extraterrestrial life after going through hypnosis to recall this lost memory.
Elena begins....
I was now nine years old and with my granny and my younger sister,
we were admiring the starry sky by the bedroom window. The Ufo changed color and shot off,
zigzagging at a tremendous speed, but it came back , that night.... Two of them appeared in
my bedroom that night, in total silence, smoothly, cunningly, and they seized me.
They took me by my arms. Their fingers hurt and bruised my flesh. I was unable to speak,
shout or move. I tried to fight them but they were holding me strong and then, the whole room
started spinning and I realized they were taking me through a vortex of lights and colors.
I was thrown onto a cold hard floor. This new place was dark and freezing cold. I started
crying, so they squeezed my forearm harder. It hurt so much, sobs dried in my throat. I could
see they were not like the ones who took me when I was a baby. These ones looked different, slightly
taller, with a wider skull and these big almond shaped obsidian eyes. They were glossy black
suits, like vinyl. They were cold, emotionless, and they dragged me onto a narrow medical table.
I noticed glowing machines around it. They tied me by the ankles, forearms and neck. Why were
they doing to me? They removed my clothes fast and mechanically. There were low screechy sound
resembling a dentist drill, approaching my head. The alien being behind me grabbed my
chin to main my head still and straight and with the drill, inserted something in my skull.
Now... They were looking between my legs... I could not move my nervous system paralyzed.
They moved very fast, as if they were in a hurry. One of them put large straps around
my wrists and when tightened them, I could feel the sharp pain being caused to the flesh of my
wrists. There were thin wires coming out of these straps, connecting to some devices on the side,
and it seemed to me there was liquid passing through these tiny needles into my blood. It
was a cold, freezing liquid and my whole body shivered. They inserted something in my private
parts with a long metallic object. The metal was so cold, but the excruciating sensation was
like a burning fire. I could see a light glowing under the skin of my belly. They acted very fast,
their moves were so weirdly mechanical. I was bleeding now, because I could feel the
hot liquid pouring out of my womb. They had no consideration, I was just like a piece of
meat. They think we have no soul, that we are so inferior to them. They spoke to each other but
it was not a language it was more like sounds, crackling, creaking insectoid sounds.
They started to now louder and with more agitation. Something was wrong.... Another
one appeared on the right; he was like them but seemed slightly different. He was bigger
and more expressive, as if he was a real person and the others some sort of robots,
or clones, or organic machines. This big one seemed worried and angry. Two of them left
the room and this big one started urging the two who stayed to hastily remove my ties. The straps
left bleeding triangular marks on my wrists. They needed to be quick, quick and suddenly, there was
this big light and the whole structure trembled. I could not move and it was terrifying. The walls,
the ground, everything trembled again, and violent vibrations shook the entire room.
They were not happy with that. What was going on? The bigger gray creature, who seemed to be
their supervisor, shouted orders in his weird language while sounds and lightning's behind
the other side of the door were getting louder. Now, I could hear shouts of human voices! The two
small grays were confused and their chief seemed furious. He pulled from his shouting again and the
door brutally exploded! I was so scared! What was going on? I couldn't move! Two tall men in space
suits rushed in, wearing helmets. I couldn't see their faces because of the lights reflection and
the smoke. A fight with some sort of laser guns engaged and one of the men lifted the taller
gray who seemed in charge, then he strangled him to death; All the other ones were shot in
the head. The same man who had strangled to death the captain of the gray beings, lifted me from the
table in his arms. My body was not responding and I was feeling cold, so cold. I could not
see their faces due to reflections of the glass helmets. There were flashes of light again coming
from the hole in the wall left by the blast of the explosion The men rushed with me through it,
moving in a hurry. All I could see was the spacesuit of my rescuer and feel it's cold plastic
material. There was a buzzing blinding blue light and then we rushed into an airlock.
It was very strange because I could see the stars around us, but we were inside some of
corridor. It seemed like we were suddenly in a different ship. They rushed into a room bathed
with bright light and laid me down on a table that lifted from the floor. It was warm in here.... I
was feeling safe. There was a woman in that room. She didn't wear a spacesuit and she was beautiful
with straight blonde hair and vibrant, huge green eyes. She wore a skin tight blue suit,
slightly glistening in the artificial light, and her body was slim and harmonious. She was looking
at me with concern and I could feel tension emanating from her. After they laid me on this
bench, the men removed their helmets but I still couldn't see their faces because they were out of
my vision. Nonetheless, I had time to notice they were blonde like her, tall and athletic.
The woman rapidly cleaned the blood off my tiny body. I let her proceed while releasing my fear,
letting go of all tensions and stress..... The man who saved my life removed his space suit's jacket
and covered me with it. It felt so warm.... He had wavy hair, and the other one long and
straight hair. I felt one of men's hands pressing my leg and saying few words in a strange language.
I was now in good hands, I knew it. These people had rescued me. There was agitation in the room,
the woman was feeling nervous and the sense of emergency was filling the air stressfully.
The gracious woman leaned over me gently grabbed my face between her hands. She spoke to me in a
strange and harmonious language which I couldn't understand but it seemed, I could feel it, that
she tried to calm me down. The two men had stepped back and she laid her hands on my shoulders.
Her energy felt warm and soothing and poured inside of my tiny body like a delightful waterfall
of calmness.... This was my first contact with Myrah, The mysterious and mesmerizing alien lady
who had looked after me all my life besides Thor Han. Their expressions were concerned and grave,
and I could see shadows of worry on the lady's pristine face. Her eyes were truly fascinating;
they had this crsytalline emerald spark. She was smaller than the two other men, and had high
prominent cheek bones, on a triangular face with a narrow chin. It seemed to me that she was from
a different race than the two other ones, as her face structure was dissimilar to her companions.
She obviously was of a smaller species. I would also learn later that I was right to think so;
these two handsome men were from the pleiades and she was from the Sirius B system. All three
of them, despite their non-terrestrial origin. Their eyes were wider proportionally to ours
and with a metallic luminosity to them. They had high cheek bones and their bodies looked
very fit. I couldn't see where the men had gone to, but I could hear and sense them in the room.
Still, my body wasn't responding to my will; I guessed the product I had
been injected with needed to dissolve and then I fell into deep asleep.....
